> "What `Image` implementation is it?"

@BendingBender this is for nodejs, where you have to use the `Image` implementation from [node-canvas](https://npm.im/canvas). 

node-canvas's `Image` accepts `string | Buffer` - [see here](https://github.com/Automattic/node-canvas/blob/master/types/index.d.ts#L232-L236)

